  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6826.34 sitting just below the massive +196M GEX wall at 6830 and above the flip strike at 6818, dealers are currently long gamma and will sell any push toward 6830 while buying dips toward 6820. The heavy positive gamma concentration between 6820-6850 creates a strong gravitational pull that should contain volatility and promote mean reversion within this range. Watch 6818 as the critical flip level - a break below shifts dealers to short gamma and accelerates selling pressure toward the 6770 negative gamma magnet.\n\n**Bottom line:** expect price to stay pinned between 6820-6830 with limited upside past the big gamma wall.",
